data.description: Welcome to 11531 Pine Tree Place in the beautiful Forest Park subdivision.  Built by Bob Schmidt Builders, this highly sought after home resides on a cul de sac and boasts 3 bedrooms, including the primary bedroom with en suite.  All three bedrooms have sliding glass doors that lead out onto the beautiful courtyard with a stamped concrete patio.  The home has 2-1/2 bathrooms and a huge family room with wood burning fireplace and a beautiful wall of cabinets.  All of the big ticket items are new, including two new Heat Pumps 2020, A/C 2020, Water Heater 2021 (the home has 2 water heaters, only one was replaced in 2021) new roof 2016.  The home needs new carpet and is priced accordingly.
